// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
// FASAL SATHI - PRISMA SCHEMA
// Database: SQLite
// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

generator client {
  provider = "prisma-client-js"
}

datasource db {
  provider = "sqlite"
  url      = env("DATABASE_URL")
}

// ━━━━━━━━━━ USER MODEL ━━━━━━━━━━
model User {
  id           String   @id @default(uuid())
  name         String
  email        String   @unique
  phone        String?  @unique
  password     String
  role         String   @default("Farmer") // SuperAdmin, Moderator, Seller, Farmer
  profileImage String?
  state        String?
  district     String?
  crops        String?  // Comma-separated crop names
  isBlocked    Boolean  @default(false)
  isVerified   Boolean  @default(false)
  fcmToken     String?  // Firebase Cloud Messaging token
  lastLoginAt  DateTime?
  createdAt    DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt    DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  seller         Seller?
  chats          Chat[]
  orders         Order[]
  reviews        Review[]
  notifications  Notification[]
  supportTickets SupportTicket[]
  weatherLogs    WeatherLog[]
  reports        Report[]

  @@map("users")
}

// ━━━━━━━━━━ SELLER MODEL ━━━━━━━━━━
model Seller {
  id            String   @id @default(uuid())
  userId        String   @unique
  businessName  String
  businessType  String?
  gstNumber     String?
  address       String?
  description   String?
  isApproved    Boolean  @default(false)
  rating        Float    @default(0)
  totalSales    Int      @default(0)
  totalRevenue  Float    @default(0)
  createdAt     DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt     DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  user     User      @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  products Product[]

  @@map("sellers")
}

// ━━━━━━━━━━ PRODUCT MODEL ━━━━━━━━━━
model Product {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  sellerId    String
  name        String
  description String?
  price       Float
  mrp         Float?
  category    String
  subCategory String?
  images      String?  // JSON array of image URLs
  stock       Int      @default(0)
  unit        String?  // kg, litre, piece, packet
  brand       String?
  isActive    Boolean  @default(true)
  isFeatured  Boolean  @default(false)
  discount    Float?   @default(0)
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  seller      Seller      @relation(fields: [sellerId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  orderItems  OrderItem[]
  reviews     Review[]

  @@map("products")
}

// ━━━━━━━━━━ ORDER MODEL ━━━━━━━━━━
model Order {
  id              String   @id @default(uuid())
  userId          String
  totalAmount     Float
  status          String   @default("pending") // pending, confirmed, shipped, delivered, cancelled
  paymentMethod   String?  // cod, online, upi
  paymentStatus   String   @default("pending") // pending, paid, failed, refunded
  shippingAddress String?
  notes           String?
  createdAt       DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt       DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  user       User        @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  orderItems OrderItem[]

  @@map("orders")
}

// ━━━━━━━━━━ ORDER ITEM MODEL ━━━━━━━━━━
model OrderItem {
  id        String @id @default(uuid())
  orderId   String
  productId String
  quantity  Int
  price     Float

  // Relations
  order   Order   @relation(fields: [orderId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  product Product @relation(fields: [productId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@map("order_items")
}

// ━━━━━━━━━━ CHAT MODEL ━━━━━━━━━━
model Chat {
  id        String   @id @default(uuid())
  userId    String
  message   String
  response  String?
  role      String   @default("user") // user, assistant
  category  String?  // crop, weather, scheme, general
  language  String?  @default("hi") // hi, en, mr, etc
  isStarred Boolean  @default(false)
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@map("chats")
}

// ━━━━━━━━━━ NOTIFICATION MODEL ━━━━━━━━━━
model Notification {
  id        String   @id @default(uuid())
  userId    String?
  title     String
  message   String
  type      String   @default("general") // general, weather, scheme, emergency, reminder, news
  imageUrl  String?
  isRead    Boolean  @default(false)
  isGlobal  Boolean  @default(false) // If true, sent to all users
  data      String?  // JSON extra data
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  user User? @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@map("notifications")
}

// ━━━━━━━━━━ GOVERNMENT SCHEME MODEL ━━━━━━━━━━
model GovernmentScheme {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  title       String
  description String
  ministry    String?
  eligibility String?
  benefits    String?
  state       String?  // null means all-India
  category    String?  // subsidy, loan, insurance, training
  imageUrl    String?
  pdfUrl      String?
  applyUrl    String?
  isFeatured  Boolean  @default(false)
  isActive    Boolean  @default(true)
  startDate   DateTime?
  expiryDate  DateTime?
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt

  @@map("government_schemes")
}

// ━━━━━━━━━━ MANDI PRICE MODEL ━━━━━━━━━━
model MandiPrice {
  id         String   @id @default(uuid())
  crop       String
  variety    String?
  market     String
  district   String
  state      String
  minPrice   Float
  maxPrice   Float
  modalPrice Float
  unit       String   @default("quintal")
  date       DateTime
  source     String?
  createdAt  DateTime @default(now())

  @@map("mandi_prices")
}

// ━━━━━━━━━━ NEWS ARTICLE MODEL ━━━━━━━━━━
model NewsArticle {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  title       String
  content     String
  summary     String?
  category    String?  // agriculture, weather, govt, market, technology
  imageUrl    String?
  videoUrl    String?
  source      String?
  author      String?
  isBreaking  Boolean  @default(false)
  isFeatured  Boolean  @default(false)
  isPublished Boolean  @default(true)
  views       Int      @default(0)
  publishedAt DateTime @default(now())
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt

  @@map("news_articles")
}

// ━━━━━━━━━━ WEATHER LOG MODEL ━━━━━━━━━━
model WeatherLog {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  userId      String?
  city        String
  state       String?
  temperature Float?
  humidity    Float?
  windSpeed   Float?
  condition   String?
  forecast    String?  // JSON weather forecast data
  alertType   String?  // none, warning, severe
  alertMessage String?
  date        DateTime @default(now())
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  user User? @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)

  @@map("weather_logs")
}

// ━━━━━━━━━━ REPORT MODEL ━━━━━━━━━━
model Report {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  userId      String?
  type        String   // daily, weekly, monthly, custom
  category    String?  // users, sales, crops, ai_usage
  data        String?  // JSON report data
  generatedAt DateTime @default(now())
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  user User? @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)

  @@map("reports")
}

// ━━━━━━━━━━ REVIEW MODEL ━━━━━━━━━━
model Review {
  id        String   @id @default(uuid())
  userId    String
  productId String
  rating    Int      // 1-5
  comment   String?
  images    String?  // JSON array of image URLs
  isVisible Boolean  @default(true)
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  user    User    @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  product Product @relation(fields: [productId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@map("reviews")
}

// ━━━━━━━━━━ SUPPORT TICKET MODEL ━━━━━━━━━━
model SupportTicket {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  userId      String
  subject     String
  description String
  category    String?  // account, order, technical, suggestion, complaint
  status      String   @default("open") // open, in_progress, resolved, closed
  priority    String   @default("medium") // low, medium, high, urgent
  adminReply  String?
  attachments String?  // JSON array of file URLs
  resolvedAt  DateTime?
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@map("support_tickets")
}
